@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zxebim(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 / 0.35)
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.19 / v0 + 0.48) * 0.10) / tmp)
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.67)) - ((v0 + 0.07 / tmp + 0.71) + (tmp + 0.31 / v2 + 0.79)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
